name: 10/23/2025 8:57 AM Real NeuralNet Stock Market Simulator
description: A simulation of a stock market with 20 stocks and 10 AI investors. Features an accurate Washington State tax model, including a 7% long-term capital gains tax with an annual exemption, and a sector-specific Business & Occupation (B&O) tax that acts as a drag on corporate growth. Watch AIs trade and manage their portfolios in real-time.
